{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "后王命冢宰，降德于眾兆民。", "text_normalized": "后王命冢宰，降德于眾兆民。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "子事父母，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰笄總，拂髦冠緌纓，端韠紳，搢笏。左右佩用，左佩紛帨、刀、礪、小觿、金燧，右佩玦、捍、管、遰、大觿、木燧，偪，屨著綦。", "text_normalized": "子事父母，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰笄總，拂髦冠緌纓，端韠紳，搢笏。左右佩用，左佩紛帨、刀、礪、小觿、金燧，右佩玦、捍、管、遰、大觿、木燧，偪，屨著綦。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "婦事舅姑，如事父母。雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰，笄總，衣紳。左佩紛帨、刀、礪、小觿、金燧，右佩箴、管、線、纊，施縏帙，大觿、木燧、衿纓，綦屨。", "text_normalized": "婦事舅姑，如事父母。雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰，笄總，衣紳。左佩紛帨、刀、礪、小觿、金燧，右佩箴、管、線、纊，施縏帙，大觿、木燧、衿纓，綦屨。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "以適父母舅姑之所，及所，下氣怡聲，問衣燠寒，疾痛苛癢，而敬抑搔之。出入，則或先或後，而敬扶持之。進盥，少者奉盤，長者奉水，請沃盥，盥卒授巾。問所欲而敬進之，柔色以溫之，饘酏、酒醴、芼羹、菽麥、蕡稻、黍粱、秫唯所欲，棗、栗、飴、蜜以甘之，堇、荁、枌、榆免槁薧滫以滑之，脂膏以膏之，父母舅姑必嘗之而後退。", "text_normalized": "以適父母舅姑之所，及所，下氣怡聲，問衣燠寒，疾痛苛癢，而敬抑搔之。出入，則或先或後，而敬扶持之。進盥，少者奉盤，長者奉水，請沃盥，盥卒授巾。問所欲而敬進之，柔色以溫之，饘酏、酒醴、芼羹、菽麥、蕡稻、黍粱、秫唯所欲，棗、栗、飴、蜜以甘之，堇、荁、枌、榆免槁薧滫以滑之，脂膏以膏之，父母舅姑必嘗之而後退。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "男女未冠笄者，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰，拂髦總角，衿纓，皆佩容臭，昧爽而朝，問何食飲矣。若已食則退，若未食則佐長者視具。", "text_normalized": "男女未冠笄者，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，櫛縰，拂髦總角，衿纓，皆佩容臭，昧爽而朝，問何食飲矣。若已食則退，若未食則佐長者視具。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "凡內外，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，衣服，斂枕簟，灑掃室堂及庭，布席，各從其事。", "text_normalized": "凡內外，雞初鳴，咸盥漱，衣服，斂枕簟，灑掃室堂及庭，布席，各從其事。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "孺子蚤寢晏起，唯所欲，食無時。", "text_normalized": "孺子蚤寢晏起，唯所欲，食無時。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "由命士以上，父子皆異宮。昧爽而朝，慈以旨甘，日出而退，各從其事，日入而夕，慈以旨甘。", "text_normalized": "由命士以上，父子皆異宮。昧爽而朝，慈以旨甘，日出而退，各從其事，日入而夕，慈以旨甘。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "父母舅姑將坐，奉席請何鄉；將衽，長者奉席請何趾。少者執床與坐，御者舉几，斂席與簟，縣衾篋枕，斂簟而襡之。", "text_normalized": "父母舅姑將坐，奉席請何鄉；將衽，長者奉席請何趾。少者執床與坐，御者舉几，斂席與簟，縣衾篋枕，斂簟而襡之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "父母舅姑之衣衾簟席枕几不傳，杖屨只敬之，勿敢近。敦牟卮匜，非餕莫敢用；與恒食飲，非餕，莫之敢飲食。", "text_normalized": "父母舅姑之衣衾簟席枕几不傳，杖屨只敬之，勿敢近。敦牟卮匜，非餕莫敢用；與恒食飲，非餕，莫之敢飲食。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "父母在，朝夕恒食，子婦佐餕，既食恒餕，父沒母存，冢子御食，群子婦佐餕如初，旨甘柔滑，孺子餕。", "text_normalized": "父母在，朝夕恒食，子婦佐餕，既食恒餕，父沒母存，冢子御食，群子婦佐餕如初，旨甘柔滑，孺子餕。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "在父母舅姑之所，有命之，應唯敬對。進退周旋慎齊，升降出入揖游，不敢噦噫、嚏咳、欠伸、跛倚、睇視，不敢唾洟；寒不敢襲，癢不敢搔；不有敬事，不敢袒裼，不涉不撅，褻衣衾不見里。", "text_normalized": "在父母舅姑之所，有命之，應唯敬對。進退周旋慎齊，升降出入揖游，不敢噦噫、嚏咳、欠伸、跛倚、睇視，不敢唾洟；寒不敢襲，癢不敢搔；不有敬事，不敢袒裼，不涉不撅，褻衣衾不見里。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 13", "sort_key": "0013", "text_original": "父母唾洟不見，冠帶垢，和灰請漱；衣裳垢，和灰請浣；衣裳綻裂，紉箴請補綴。五日，則燂湯請浴，三日具沐，其間面垢，燂潘請靧；足垢，燂湯請洗。少事長，賤事貴，共帥時。", "text_normalized": "父母唾洟不見，冠帶垢，和灰請漱；衣裳垢，和灰請浣；衣裳綻裂，紉箴請補綴。五日，則燂湯請浴，三日具沐，其間面垢，燂潘請靧；足垢，燂湯請洗。少事長，賤事貴，共帥時。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 14", "sort_key": "0014", "text_original": "男不言內，女不言外。非祭非喪，不相授器。其相授，則女受以篚，其無篚則皆坐奠之而後取之。外內不共井，不共湢浴，不通寢席，不通乞假，男女不通衣裳，內言不出，外言不入。", "text_normalized": "男不言內，女不言外。非祭非喪，不相授器。其相授，則女受以篚，其無篚則皆坐奠之而後取之。外內不共井，不共湢浴，不通寢席，不通乞假，男女不通衣裳，內言不出，外言不入。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 15", "sort_key": "0015", "text_original": "男子入內，不嘯不指，夜行以燭，無燭則止。女子出門，必擁蔽其面，夜行以燭，無燭則止。道路：男子由右，女子由左。", "text_normalized": "男子入內，不嘯不指，夜行以燭，無燭則止。女子出門，必擁蔽其面，夜行以燭，無燭則止。道路：男子由右，女子由左。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 16", "sort_key": "0016", "text_original": "子婦孝者、敬者，父母舅姑之命，勿逆勿怠。若飲食之，雖不耆，必嘗而待；加之衣服，雖不欲，必服而待；加之事，人待之，己雖弗欲，姑與之，而姑使之，而後復之。", "text_normalized": "子婦孝者、敬者，父母舅姑之命，勿逆勿怠。若飲食之，雖不耆，必嘗而待；加之衣服，雖不欲，必服而待；加之事，人待之，己雖弗欲，姑與之，而姑使之，而後復之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 17", "sort_key": "0017", "text_original": "子婦有勤勞之事，雖甚愛之，姑縱之，而寧數休之。子婦未孝未敬，勿庸疾怨，姑教之；若不可教，而後怒之；不可怒，子放婦出，而不表禮焉。", "text_normalized": "子婦有勤勞之事，雖甚愛之，姑縱之，而寧數休之。子婦未孝未敬，勿庸疾怨，姑教之；若不可教，而後怒之；不可怒，子放婦出，而不表禮焉。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 18", "sort_key": "0018", "text_original": "父母有過，下氣怡色，柔聲以諫。諫若不入，起敬起孝，說則復諫；不說，與其得罪於鄉黨州閭，寧孰諫。父母怒、不說，而撻之流血，不敢疾怨，起敬起孝。", "text_normalized": "父母有過，下氣怡色，柔聲以諫。諫若不入，起敬起孝，說則復諫；不說，與其得罪於鄉黨州閭，寧孰諫。父母怒、不說，而撻之流血，不敢疾怨，起敬起孝。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 19", "sort_key": "0019", "text_original": "父母有婢子若庶子、庶孫，甚愛之，雖父母沒，沒身敬之不衰。", "text_normalized": "父母有婢子若庶子、庶孫，甚愛之，雖父母沒，沒身敬之不衰。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 20", "sort_key": "0020", "text_original": "子有二妾，父母愛一人焉，子愛一人焉，由衣服飲食，由執事，毋敢視父母所愛，雖父母沒不衰。子甚宜其妻，父母不說，出；子不宜其妻，父母曰：「是善事我。」子行夫婦之禮焉，沒身不衰。", "text_normalized": "子有二妾，父母愛一人焉，子愛一人焉，由衣服飲食，由執事，毋敢視父母所愛，雖父母沒不衰。子甚宜其妻，父母不說，出；子不宜其妻，父母曰：「是善事我。」子行夫婦之禮焉，沒身不衰。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 21", "sort_key": "0021", "text_original": "父母雖沒，將為善，思貽父母令名，必果；將為不善，思貽父母羞辱，必不果。", "text_normalized": "父母雖沒，將為善，思貽父母令名，必果；將為不善，思貽父母羞辱，必不果。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 22", "sort_key": "0022", "text_original": "舅沒則姑老，冢婦所祭祀、賓客，每事必請於姑，介婦請於冢婦。舅姑使冢婦，毋怠，不友無禮於介婦。舅姑若使介婦，毋敢敵耦於冢婦，不敢并行，不敢并命，不敢并坐。", "text_normalized": "舅沒則姑老，冢婦所祭祀、賓客，每事必請於姑，介婦請於冢婦。舅姑使冢婦，毋怠，不友無禮於介婦。舅姑若使介婦，毋敢敵耦於冢婦，不敢并行，不敢并命，不敢并坐。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 23", "sort_key": "0023", "text_original": "凡婦，不命適私室，不敢退。婦將有事，大小必請於舅姑。子婦無私貨，無私畜，無私器，不敢私假，不敢私與。婦或賜之飲食、衣服、布帛、佩帨、茝蘭，則受而獻諸舅姑，舅姑受之則喜，如新受賜，若反賜之則辭，不得命，如更受賜，藏以待乏。婦若有私親兄弟將與之，則必復請其故，賜而後與之。", "text_normalized": "凡婦，不命適私室，不敢退。婦將有事，大小必請於舅姑。子婦無私貨，無私畜，無私器，不敢私假，不敢私與。婦或賜之飲食、衣服、布帛、佩帨、茝蘭，則受而獻諸舅姑，舅姑受之則喜，如新受賜，若反賜之則辭，不得命，如更受賜，藏以待乏。婦若有私親兄弟將與之，則必復請其故，賜而後與之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 24", "sort_key": "0024", "text_original": "適子庶子只事宗子宗婦。雖貴富，不敢以貴富入宗子之家，雖眾車徒舍於外，以寡約入。", "text_normalized": "適子庶子只事宗子宗婦。雖貴富，不敢以貴富入宗子之家，雖眾車徒舍於外，以寡約入。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 25", "sort_key": "0025", "text_original": "子弟猶歸器衣服裘衾車馬，則必獻其上，而後敢服用其次也；若非所獻，則不敢以入於宗子之門，不敢以貴富加於父兄宗族。若富，則具二牲，獻其賢者於宗子，夫婦皆齊而宗敬焉，終事而後敢私祭。", "text_normalized": "子弟猶歸器衣服裘衾車馬，則必獻其上，而後敢服用其次也；若非所獻，則不敢以入於宗子之門，不敢以貴富加於父兄宗族。若富，則具二牲，獻其賢者於宗子，夫婦皆齊而宗敬焉，終事而後敢私祭。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 26", "sort_key": "0026", "text_original": "飯：黍，稷，稻，粱，白黍，黃粱，稰，穛。", "text_normalized": "飯：黍，稷，稻，粱，白黍，黃粱，稰，穛。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 27", "sort_key": "0027", "text_original": "膳：膷，臐，膮，醢，牛炙。醢，牛胾，醢，牛膾。羊炙，羊胾，醢，豕炙。醢，豕胾，芥醬，魚膾。雉，兔，鶉，鷃。", "text_normalized": "膳：膷，臐，膮，醢，牛炙。醢，牛胾，醢，牛膾。羊炙，羊胾，醢，豕炙。醢，豕胾，芥醬，魚膾。雉，兔，鶉，鷃。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "飲：重醴，稻醴清糟，黍醴清糟，粱醴清糟，或以酏為醴，黍酏，漿，水，醷，濫。", "text_normalized": "飲：重醴，稻醴清糟，黍醴清糟，粱醴清糟，或以酏為醴，黍酏，漿，水，醷，濫。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "酒：清、白。", "text_normalized": "酒：清、白。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "羞：糗，餌，粉，酏。", "text_normalized": "羞：糗，餌，粉，酏。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "食：蝸醢而菰食，雉羹；麥食，脯羹，雞羹；析稌，犬羹，兔羹；和糝不蓼。", "text_normalized": "食：蝸醢而菰食，雉羹；麥食，脯羹，雞羹；析稌，犬羹，兔羹；和糝不蓼。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "濡豚，包苦實蓼；濡雞，醢醬實蓼；濡魚，卵醬實蓼；濡鱉，醢醬實蓼。", "text_normalized": "濡豚，包苦實蓼；濡雞，醢醬實蓼；濡魚，卵醬實蓼；濡鱉，醢醬實蓼。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 33", "sort_key": "0033", "text_original": "腶修，蚳醢，脯羹，兔醢，糜膚，魚醢，魚膾，芥醬，麋腥，醢，醬，桃諸，梅諸，卵鹽。", "text_normalized": "腶修，蚳醢，脯羹，兔醢，糜膚，魚醢，魚膾，芥醬，麋腥，醢，醬，桃諸，梅諸，卵鹽。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 34", "sort_key": "0034", "text_original": "凡食齊視春時，羹齊視夏時，醬齊視秋時，飲齊視冬時。", "text_normalized": "凡食齊視春時，羹齊視夏時，醬齊視秋時，飲齊視冬時。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 35", "sort_key": "0035", "text_original": "凡和，春多酸，夏多苦，秋多辛，冬多鹹，調以滑甘。", "text_normalized": "凡和，春多酸，夏多苦，秋多辛，冬多鹹，調以滑甘。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 36", "sort_key": "0036", "text_original": "牛宜稌，羊宜黍，豕宜稷，犬宜粱，雁宜麥，魚宜菰。", "text_normalized": "牛宜稌，羊宜黍，豕宜稷，犬宜粱，雁宜麥，魚宜菰。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 37", "sort_key": "0037", "text_original": "春宜羔豚膳膏薌，夏宜腒鱐膳膏臊，秋宜犢麑膳膏腥，冬宜鮮羽膳膏膻。", "text_normalized": "春宜羔豚膳膏薌，夏宜腒鱐膳膏臊，秋宜犢麑膳膏腥，冬宜鮮羽膳膏膻。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 38", "sort_key": "0038", "text_original": "牛修，鹿脯，田豕脯，糜脯，麇脯，麋、鹿、田豕、麇，皆有軒，雉兔皆有芼。爵，鷃，蜩，范，芝栭，菱，椇，棗，栗，榛，柿，瓜，桃，李，梅，杏，楂，梨，姜，桂。", "text_normalized": "牛修，鹿脯，田豕脯，糜脯，麇脯，麋、鹿、田豕、麇，皆有軒，雉兔皆有芼。爵，鷃，蜩，范，芝栭，菱，椇，棗，栗，榛，柿，瓜，桃，李，梅，杏，楂，梨，姜，桂。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 39", "sort_key": "0039", "text_original": "大夫燕食，有膾無脯，有脯無膾。士不貳羹胾，庶人耆老不徒食。", "text_normalized": "大夫燕食，有膾無脯，有脯無膾。士不貳羹胾，庶人耆老不徒食。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 40", "sort_key": "0040", "text_original": "膾：春用蔥，秋用芥、豚；春用韭，秋用蓼。脂用蔥，膏用薤，三牲用藙，和用醯，獸用梅。鶉羹、雞羹、鴽，釀之蓼。魴鱮烝，雛燒，雉，薌無蓼。", "text_normalized": "膾：春用蔥，秋用芥、豚；春用韭，秋用蓼。脂用蔥，膏用薤，三牲用藙，和用醯，獸用梅。鶉羹、雞羹、鴽，釀之蓼。魴鱮烝，雛燒，雉，薌無蓼。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 41", "sort_key": "0041", "text_original": "不食雛鱉，狼去腸，狗去腎，貍去正脊，兔去尻，狐去首，豚去腦，魚去乙，鱉去醜。", "text_normalized": "不食雛鱉，狼去腸，狗去腎，貍去正脊，兔去尻，狐去首，豚去腦，魚去乙，鱉去醜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 42", "sort_key": "0042", "text_original": "肉曰脫之，魚曰作之，棗曰新之，栗曰撰之，桃曰膽之，柤梨曰攢之。", "text_normalized": "肉曰脫之，魚曰作之，棗曰新之，栗曰撰之，桃曰膽之，柤梨曰攢之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 43", "sort_key": "0043", "text_original": "牛夜鳴則庮，羊泠毛而毳、膻，狗赤股而躁、臊，鳥麃色而沙鳴、郁，豕望視而交睫、腥，馬黑脊而般臂、漏，雛尾不盈握弗食，舒雁翠，鵠鴞胖，舒鳧翠，雞肝，雁腎，鴇奧，鹿胃。", "text_normalized": "牛夜鳴則庮，羊泠毛而毳、膻，狗赤股而躁、臊，鳥麃色而沙鳴、郁，豕望視而交睫、腥，馬黑脊而般臂、漏，雛尾不盈握弗食，舒雁翠，鵠鴞胖，舒鳧翠，雞肝，雁腎，鴇奧，鹿胃。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 44", "sort_key": "0044", "text_original": "肉腥細者為膾，大者為軒；或曰麋鹿魚為菹，麇為辟雞，野豕為軒，兔為宛脾，切蔥若薤，實諸醯以柔之。", "text_normalized": "肉腥細者為膾，大者為軒；或曰麋鹿魚為菹，麇為辟雞，野豕為軒，兔為宛脾，切蔥若薤，實諸醯以柔之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 45", "sort_key": "0045", "text_original": "羹食，自諸侯以下至於庶人無等。", "text_normalized": "羹食，自諸侯以下至於庶人無等。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 46", "sort_key": "0046", "text_original": "大夫無秩膳，大夫七十而有閣，天子之閣。左達五，右達五，公侯伯於房中五，大夫於閣三，士於坫一。", "text_normalized": "大夫無秩膳，大夫七十而有閣，天子之閣。左達五，右達五，公侯伯於房中五，大夫於閣三，士於坫一。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 47", "sort_key": "0047", "text_original": "凡養老：有虞氏以燕禮，夏后氏以饗禮，殷人以食禮，周人修而兼用之。凡五十養於鄉，六十養於國，七十養於學，達於諸侯。八十拜君命，一坐再至，瞽亦如之，九十者使人受。五十異粻，六十宿肉，七十二膳，八十常珍，九十飲食不違寢，膳飲從於游可也。六十歲制，七十時制，八十月制，九十日修，唯絞紟衾冒，死而後制。五十始衰，六十非肉不飽，七十非帛不暖，八十非人不暖，九十雖得人不暖矣。五十杖於家，六十杖於鄉，七十杖於國，八十杖於朝，九十者天子欲有問焉，則就其室以珍從。七十不俟朝，八十月告存，九十日有秩。五十不從力政，六十不與服戎，七十不與賓客之事，八十齊喪之事弗及也。五十而爵，六十不親學，七十致政；凡自七十以上，唯衰麻為喪。", "text_normalized": "凡養老：有虞氏以燕禮，夏后氏以饗禮，殷人以食禮，周人修而兼用之。凡五十養於鄉，六十養於國，七十養於學，達於諸侯。八十拜君命，一坐再至，瞽亦如之，九十者使人受。五十異粻，六十宿肉，七十二膳，八十常珍，九十飲食不違寢，膳飲從於游可也。六十歲制，七十時制，八十月制，九十日修，唯絞紟衾冒，死而後制。五十始衰，六十非肉不飽，七十非帛不暖，八十非人不暖，九十雖得人不暖矣。五十杖於家，六十杖於鄉，七十杖於國，八十杖於朝，九十者天子欲有問焉，則就其室以珍從。七十不俟朝，八十月告存，九十日有秩。五十不從力政，六十不與服戎，七十不與賓客之事，八十齊喪之事弗及也。五十而爵，六十不親學，七十致政；凡自七十以上，唯衰麻為喪。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 48", "sort_key": "0048", "text_original": "凡三王養老皆引年，八十者一子不從政，九十者其家不從政；瞽亦如之。凡父母在，子雖老不坐。有虞氏養國老於上庠，養庶老於下庠；夏后氏養國老於東序，養庶老於西序；殷人養國老於右學，養庶老於左學；周人養國老於東膠，養庶老於虞庠，虞庠在國之西郊。有虞氏皇而祭，深衣而養老；夏后氏收而祭，燕衣而養老；殷人冔而祭，縞衣而養老；周人冕而祭，玄衣而養老。", "text_normalized": "凡三王養老皆引年，八十者一子不從政，九十者其家不從政；瞽亦如之。凡父母在，子雖老不坐。有虞氏養國老於上庠，養庶老於下庠；夏后氏養國老於東序，養庶老於西序；殷人養國老於右學，養庶老於左學；周人養國老於東膠，養庶老於虞庠，虞庠在國之西郊。有虞氏皇而祭，深衣而養老；夏后氏收而祭，燕衣而養老；殷人冔而祭，縞衣而養老；周人冕而祭，玄衣而養老。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 49", "sort_key": "0049", "text_original": "曾子曰：「孝子之養老也，樂其心不違其志，樂其耳目，安其寢處，以其飲食忠養之孝子之身終，終身也者，非終父母之身，終其身也；是故父母之所愛亦愛之，父母之所敬亦敬之，至於犬馬盡然，而況於人乎！」", "text_normalized": "曾子曰：「孝子之養老也，樂其心不違其志，樂其耳目，安其寢處，以其飲食忠養之孝子之身終，終身也者，非終父母之身，終其身也；是故父母之所愛亦愛之，父母之所敬亦敬之，至於犬馬盡然，而況於人乎！」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 50", "sort_key": "0050", "text_original": "凡養老，五帝憲，三王有乞言。五帝憲，養氣體而不乞言，有善則記之為惇史。三王亦憲，既養老而後乞言，亦微其禮，皆有惇史。", "text_normalized": "凡養老，五帝憲，三王有乞言。五帝憲，養氣體而不乞言，有善則記之為惇史。三王亦憲，既養老而後乞言，亦微其禮，皆有惇史。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 51", "sort_key": "0051", "text_original": "淳熬：煎醢，加于陸稻上，沃之以膏曰淳熬。淳毋煎醢，加于黍食上，沃之以膏曰淳毋。", "text_normalized": "淳熬：煎醢，加于陸稻上，沃之以膏曰淳熬。淳毋煎醢，加于黍食上，沃之以膏曰淳毋。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 52", "sort_key": "0052", "text_original": "炮：取豚若將，刲之刳之，實棗於其腹中，編萑以苴之，涂之以謹涂，炮之，涂皆乾，擘之，濯手以摩之，去其皽，為稻粉糔溲之以為酏，以付豚煎諸膏，膏必滅之，鉅鑊湯以小鼎薌脯於其中，使其湯毋滅鼎，三日三夜毋絕火，而後調之以醯醢。", "text_normalized": "炮：取豚若將，刲之刳之，實棗於其腹中，編萑以苴之，涂之以謹涂，炮之，涂皆乾，擘之，濯手以摩之，去其皽，為稻粉糔溲之以為酏，以付豚煎諸膏，膏必滅之，鉅鑊湯以小鼎薌脯於其中，使其湯毋滅鼎，三日三夜毋絕火，而後調之以醯醢。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 53", "sort_key": "0053", "text_original": "搗珍：取牛羊麋鹿麇之肉必脄，每物與牛若一捶，反側之，去其餌，熟出之，去其餌，柔其肉。", "text_normalized": "搗珍：取牛羊麋鹿麇之肉必脄，每物與牛若一捶，反側之，去其餌，熟出之，去其餌，柔其肉。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 54", "sort_key": "0054", "text_original": "漬：取牛肉必新殺者，薄切之，必絕其理；湛諸美酒，期朝而食之以醢若醯醷。", "text_normalized": "漬：取牛肉必新殺者，薄切之，必絕其理；湛諸美酒，期朝而食之以醢若醯醷。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 55", "sort_key": "0055", "text_original": "為熬：捶之，去其皽，編萑布牛肉焉，屑桂與姜以灑諸上而鹽之，乾而食之。施羊亦如之，施麋、施鹿、施麇皆如牛羊。欲濡肉則釋而煎之以醢，欲乾肉則捶而食之。", "text_normalized": "為熬：捶之，去其皽，編萑布牛肉焉，屑桂與姜以灑諸上而鹽之，乾而食之。施羊亦如之，施麋、施鹿、施麇皆如牛羊。欲濡肉則釋而煎之以醢，欲乾肉則捶而食之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 56", "sort_key": "0056", "text_original": "糝：取牛羊豕之肉，三如一小切之，與稻米；稻米二肉一，合以為餌煎之。", "text_normalized": "糝：取牛羊豕之肉，三如一小切之，與稻米；稻米二肉一，合以為餌煎之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 57", "sort_key": "0057", "text_original": "肝菺：取狈肝一，幪之，以其菺濡炙之，舉焦，其菺不蓼；取稻米舉糔溲之，小切狼臅膏，以與稻米為酏。", "text_normalized": "肝菺：取狈肝一，幪之，以其菺濡炙之，舉焦，其菺不蓼；取稻米舉糔溲之，小切狼臅膏，以與稻米為酏。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 58", "sort_key": "0058", "text_original": "禮，始於謹夫婦，為宮室，辨外內。男子居外，女子居內，深宮固門，閽寺守之。男不入，女不出。", "text_normalized": "禮，始於謹夫婦，為宮室，辨外內。男子居外，女子居內，深宮固門，閽寺守之。男不入，女不出。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 59", "sort_key": "0059", "text_original": "男女不同椸枷，不敢懸於夫之楎椸，不敢藏於夫之篋笥，不敢共湢浴。夫不在，斂枕篋簟席、襡器而藏之。少事長，賤事貴，咸如之。", "text_normalized": "男女不同椸枷，不敢懸於夫之楎椸，不敢藏於夫之篋笥，不敢共湢浴。夫不在，斂枕篋簟席、襡器而藏之。少事長，賤事貴，咸如之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 60", "sort_key": "0060", "text_original": "夫婦之禮，唯及七十，同藏無間。故妾雖老，年未滿五十，必與五日之御。將御者，齊，漱浣，慎衣服，櫛縰笄，總角，拂髦，衿纓綦屨。雖婢妾，衣服飲食必後長者。妻不在，妾御莫敢當夕。", "text_normalized": "夫婦之禮，唯及七十，同藏無間。故妾雖老，年未滿五十，必與五日之御。將御者，齊，漱浣，慎衣服，櫛縰笄，總角，拂髦，衿纓綦屨。雖婢妾，衣服飲食必後長者。妻不在，妾御莫敢當夕。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 61, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 61", "sort_key": "0061", "text_original": "妻將生子，及月辰，居側室，夫使人日再問之，作而自問之，妻不敢見，使姆衣服而對，至於子生，夫復使人日再問之，夫齊則不入側室之門。子生，男子設弧於門左，女子設帨於門右。三日，始負子，男射女否。", "text_normalized": "妻將生子，及月辰，居側室，夫使人日再問之，作而自問之，妻不敢見，使姆衣服而對，至於子生，夫復使人日再問之，夫齊則不入側室之門。子生，男子設弧於門左，女子設帨於門右。三日，始負子，男射女否。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 62, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 62", "sort_key": "0062", "text_original": "國君世子生，告於君，接以大牢，宰掌具。三日，卜士負之，吉者宿齊朝服寢門外，詩負之，射人以桑弧蓬矢六。射天地四方，保受乃負之，宰醴負子，賜之束帛，卜士之妻、大夫之妾，使食子。", "text_normalized": "國君世子生，告於君，接以大牢，宰掌具。三日，卜士負之，吉者宿齊朝服寢門外，詩負之，射人以桑弧蓬矢六。射天地四方，保受乃負之，宰醴負子，賜之束帛，卜士之妻、大夫之妾，使食子。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 63, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 63", "sort_key": "0063", "text_original": "凡接子，擇日，冢子則大牢，庶人特豚，士特豕，大夫少牢，國君世子大牢，其非冢子，則皆降一等。", "text_normalized": "凡接子，擇日，冢子則大牢，庶人特豚，士特豕，大夫少牢，國君世子大牢，其非冢子，則皆降一等。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 64, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 64", "sort_key": "0064", "text_original": "異為孺子室於宮中，擇於諸母與可者，必求其寬裕慈惠、溫良恭敬、慎而寡言者，使為子師，其次為慈母，其次為保母，皆居子室，他人無事不往。", "text_normalized": "異為孺子室於宮中，擇於諸母與可者，必求其寬裕慈惠、溫良恭敬、慎而寡言者，使為子師，其次為慈母，其次為保母，皆居子室，他人無事不往。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 65, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 65", "sort_key": "0065", "text_original": "三月之末，擇日剪發為鬌，男角女羈，否則男左女右。是日也，妻以子見於父，貴人則為衣服，由命士以下，皆漱浣，男女夙興，沐浴衣服，具視朔食，夫入門，升自阼階。立於阼西鄉，妻抱子出自房，當楣立東面。", "text_normalized": "三月之末，擇日剪發為鬌，男角女羈，否則男左女右。是日也，妻以子見於父，貴人則為衣服，由命士以下，皆漱浣，男女夙興，沐浴衣服，具視朔食，夫入門，升自阼階。立於阼西鄉，妻抱子出自房，當楣立東面。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 66, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 66", "sort_key": "0066", "text_original": "姆先，相曰：「母某敢用時日只見孺子。」夫對曰：「欽有帥。」父執子之右手，咳而名之。妻對曰：「記有成。」遂左還，授師，子師辯告諸婦諸母名，妻遂適寢。", "text_normalized": "姆先，相曰：「母某敢用時日只見孺子。」夫對曰：「欽有帥。」父執子之右手，咳而名之。妻對曰：「記有成。」遂左還，授師，子師辯告諸婦諸母名，妻遂適寢。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 67, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 67", "sort_key": "0067", "text_original": "夫告宰名，宰辯告諸男名，書曰：「某年某月某日某生。」而藏之，宰告閭史，閭史書為二，其一藏諸閭府，其一獻諸州史；州史獻諸州伯，州伯命藏諸州府。夫入食如養禮。", "text_normalized": "夫告宰名，宰辯告諸男名，書曰：「某年某月某日某生。」而藏之，宰告閭史，閭史書為二，其一藏諸閭府，其一獻諸州史；州史獻諸州伯，州伯命藏諸州府。夫入食如養禮。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 68, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 68", "sort_key": "0068", "text_original": "世子生，則君沐浴朝服，夫人亦如之，皆立於阼階西鄉，世婦抱子升自西階，君名之，乃降。", "text_normalized": "世子生，則君沐浴朝服，夫人亦如之，皆立於阼階西鄉，世婦抱子升自西階，君名之，乃降。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 69, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 69", "sort_key": "0069", "text_original": "適子庶子見於外寢，撫其首咳而名之，禮帥初，無辭。", "text_normalized": "適子庶子見於外寢，撫其首咳而名之，禮帥初，無辭。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 70, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 70", "sort_key": "0070", "text_original": "凡名子，不以日月，不以國，不以隱疾；大夫、士之子，不敢與世子同名。", "text_normalized": "凡名子，不以日月，不以國，不以隱疾；大夫、士之子，不敢與世子同名。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 71, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 71", "sort_key": "0071", "text_original": "妾將生子，及月辰，夫使人日一問之。子生三月之末，漱浣夙齊，見於內寢，禮之如始入室；君已食，徹焉，使之特餕，遂入御。", "text_normalized": "妾將生子，及月辰，夫使人日一問之。子生三月之末，漱浣夙齊，見於內寢，禮之如始入室；君已食，徹焉，使之特餕，遂入御。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 72, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 72", "sort_key": "0072", "text_original": "公庶子生，就側室。三月之末，其母沐浴朝服見於君，擯者以其子見，君所有賜，君名之。眾子，則使有司名之。", "text_normalized": "公庶子生，就側室。三月之末，其母沐浴朝服見於君，擯者以其子見，君所有賜，君名之。眾子，則使有司名之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 73, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 73", "sort_key": "0073", "text_original": "庶人無側室者，及月辰，夫出居群室，其問之也，與子見父之禮，無以異也。", "text_normalized": "庶人無側室者，及月辰，夫出居群室，其問之也，與子見父之禮，無以異也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 74, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 74", "sort_key": "0074", "text_original": "凡父在，孫見於祖，祖亦名之，禮如子見父，無辭。", "text_normalized": "凡父在，孫見於祖，祖亦名之，禮如子見父，無辭。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 75, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 75", "sort_key": "0075", "text_original": "食子者，三年而出，見於公宮則劬。大夫之子有食母，士之妻自養其子。", "text_normalized": "食子者，三年而出，見於公宮則劬。大夫之子有食母，士之妻自養其子。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 76, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 76", "sort_key": "0076", "text_original": "由命士以上及大夫之子，旬而見。冢子未食而見，必執其右手，適子庶子已食而見，必循其首。", "text_normalized": "由命士以上及大夫之子，旬而見。冢子未食而見，必執其右手，適子庶子已食而見，必循其首。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 77, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 77", "sort_key": "0077", "text_original": "子能食食，教以右手。能言，男唯女俞。男鞶革，女鞶絲。", "text_normalized": "子能食食，教以右手。能言，男唯女俞。男鞶革，女鞶絲。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 78, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 78", "sort_key": "0078", "text_original": "六年教之數與方名。七年男女不同席，不共食。八年出入門戶及即席飲食，必後長者，始教之讓。九年教之數日。", "text_normalized": "六年教之數與方名。七年男女不同席，不共食。八年出入門戶及即席飲食，必後長者，始教之讓。九年教之數日。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 79, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 79", "sort_key": "0079", "text_original": "十年出就外傅，居宿於外，學書計，衣不帛襦褲，禮帥初，朝夕學幼儀，請肄簡諒。", "text_normalized": "十年出就外傅，居宿於外，學書計，衣不帛襦褲，禮帥初，朝夕學幼儀，請肄簡諒。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 80, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 80", "sort_key": "0080", "text_original": "十有三年學樂，誦《詩》，舞《勺》，成童舞《象》，學射御。二十而冠，始學禮，可以衣裘帛，舞《大夏》，惇行孝弟，博學不教，內而不出。", "text_normalized": "十有三年學樂，誦《詩》，舞《勺》，成童舞《象》，學射御。二十而冠，始學禮，可以衣裘帛，舞《大夏》，惇行孝弟，博學不教，內而不出。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 81, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 81", "sort_key": "0081", "text_original": "三十而有室，始理男事，博學無方，孫友視志。四十始仕，方物出謀發慮，道合則服從，不可則去。五十命為大夫，服官政。七十致事。凡男拜，尚左手。", "text_normalized": "三十而有室，始理男事，博學無方，孫友視志。四十始仕，方物出謀發慮，道合則服從，不可則去。五十命為大夫，服官政。七十致事。凡男拜，尚左手。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 82, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 82", "sort_key": "0082", "text_original": "女子十年不出，姆教婉娩聽從，執麻枲，治絲繭，織紝組紃，學女事以共衣服，觀於祭祀，納酒漿、籩豆、菹醢，禮相助奠。", "text_normalized": "女子十年不出，姆教婉娩聽從，執麻枲，治絲繭，織紝組紃，學女事以共衣服，觀於祭祀，納酒漿、籩豆、菹醢，禮相助奠。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family", "source_id": "liji-012-the-pattern-of-the-family__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 83, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《內則》 83", "sort_key": "0083", "text_original": "十有五年而笄，二十而嫁；有故，二十三年而嫁。聘則為妻，奔則為妾。凡女拜尚右手。", "text_normalized": "十有五年而笄，二十而嫁；有故，二十三年而嫁。聘則為妻，奔則為妾。凡女拜尚右手。", "notes": ""}
